function generatePixelMapForSize(pm) pms={} for y=1,5 do for x=1,4 do if pm[math.floor(0.5+y)] and pm[math.floor(0.5+y)][math.floor(0.5+x)] then table.insert(pms,{x=x,y=y}) end end end return pms end
